name: Mundoteam
description: Mundoteam seeks to be a fully community-based decentralized currency and end 100% decentralization. One of the many objectives is also to obtain profitability through low-price, high-reward mining. Mundoteam will once again change the world of mining towards profitability in addition to depending on itself. We live in a world where everything is centralized where the poor are poorer and the rich are richer and mundoteam wants to change the system from decentralization 20 years support the mundoteam group on the network
